flowchart LR
  P[Patient speech or pharmacist keywords] --> UI[Pharmacist PWA]
  UI --> N[Normalizer and slot extractor\nWeb Worker]
  N --> S[Deterministic safety gate]
  S --> R[In-memory alias trie + rules + BM25]
  R --> C[Instant consultation card]
  C --> UI

  UI -. push-to-talk audio .-> RT[OpenAI Realtime transcription\ngpt-realtime-whisper]
  RT -. transcript deltas .-> N

  C -. optional structured context .-> API[Fastify API]
  API --> RED[PHI redactor]
  RED --> RESP[OpenAI Responses API\nGPT-5.6 Luna/Terra]
  RESP --> API
  API --> UI

  K[Offline knowledge compiler] --> V[Pharmacist review + official verification]
  V --> PACK[Signed immutable knowledge pack]
  PACK --> R
  PACK --> API

  API --> AUDIT[Coded audit and latency events\nNo raw audio/transcript]
  ADMIN[Reviewer console] --> K
  OFFICIAL[MFDS / HIRA DUR / approved evidence] --> V
